

Introducing the XX Game Console: the first gaming console designed to take your gaming performance to unprecedented heights. We’ve taken the technology and innovations from the powerful gaming PCs and combined them into a single console introducing the all-in-one gaming package.

Experience superior graphics and game play with ultra-performance power, providing Lag and Stutter free gaming environments. The XX Game Console includes a massive range of content including console exclusive titles and downloadable content. With revolutionary features such as the Cloud streaming, enjoy the latest game and never worry about choppy game play as we’ll be able to predict your gaming performance and make dynamic improvements as you play.

The XX Game Console has been designed with gamers in mind. Built for speed, the intuitive user interface is engineered to be intuitive and responsive, so no matter your skill levels you can navigate through menus swiftly and access the content you want in a matter of seconds. Co-op or go online and battle friends or foes in the Arena.

For the ultimate gaming performance, pair the XX Game Console with the xxPront Controller. This controller is packed with features to improve playability. The enhanced buil-in vibration motors, triggers provide haptic feedback, and there’s even motion control support.

Make the XX Game Console the centerpoint of your entertainment center and enjoy the ultimate gaming experience - only on the XX Game Console. Unleash your gaming power today.